<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>中国新闻|今日突发新闻|路透社</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/</link><description>Reuters.com 是您获取最新中国新闻故事和时事的在线来源，确保我们的读者及时了解任何突发新闻动态 - RSSHub 用爱制作(https://github.com/DIYgod/RSSHub)</description><lastBuildDate>Sat, 11 May 2024 00:52:58 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>美国在气候谈判中讨论了中国太阳能制造和煤炭的“产能过剩”</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/sustainability/climate-energy/us-discussed-overcapacity-chinese-solar-manufacturing-coal-climate-talks-2024-05-10/</link><description>美国国务院高级官员周五表示，美国和中国在为期两天的气候变化双边会议上讨论了中国太阳能和电池制造、钢铁生产和煤炭发电的产能过剩问题。</description><pubDate>Fri, 10 May 2024 18:24:37 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/sustainability/climate-energy/us-discussed-overcapacity-chinese-solar-manufacturing-coal-climate-talks-2024-05-10/</guid></item><item><title>中国央行承诺支持经济复苏</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/chinas-central-bank-pledges-support-economic-recovery-2024-05-10/</link><description>中国央行周五表示，将确保流动性合理充裕和信贷扩张，巩固经济复苏，但经济复苏仍面临诸多挑战。</description><pubDate>Fri, 10 May 2024 17:17:28 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/chinas-central-bank-pledges-support-economic-recovery-2024-05-10/</guid></item><item><title>独家：消息人士称，在美国上市面临障碍的情况下，Shein 加强了伦敦 IPO 的准备工作</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/deals/shein-steps-up-london-ipo-preparations-amid-us-hurdles-listing-sources-say-2024-05-10/</link><description>两位知情人士表示，快时尚巨头 Shein 正在加紧准备在伦敦上市，此前该公司试图在纽约上市，但面临监管障碍和美国立法者的阻力。</description><pubDate>Fri, 10 May 2024 16:01:37 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/deals/shein-steps-up-london-ipo-preparations-amid-us-hurdles-listing-sources-say-2024-05-10/</guid></item><item><title>独家：拜登将对中国医疗用品征收关税——消息人士</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/us/biden-put-tariffs-china-medical-supplies-sources-2024-05-10/</link><description>据两位知情人士透露，拜登政府预计将在下周公布新的贸易战略时对注射器和个人防护设备等中国制造的医疗设备征收新的关税。</description><pubDate>Fri, 10 May 2024 15:42:28 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/us/biden-put-tariffs-china-medical-supplies-sources-2024-05-10/</guid></item><item><title>美国修改限制药明康德和中国生物科技公司的法案，给予更多时间切断联系</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/technology/us-bill-restrict-wuxi-apptec-other-chinese-biotech-cos-revised-give-more-time-2024-05-10/</link><description>新版国会法案将限制美国与包括药明康德和华大基因在内的某些中国生物科技公司开展业务，该法案将要求美国公司在 2032 年之前终止与这些公司的合作，从而延长寻找新合作伙伴的时间。</description><pubDate>Fri, 10 May 2024 14:50:41 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/technology/us-bill-restrict-wuxi-apptec-other-chinese-biotech-cos-revised-give-more-time-2024-05-10/</guid></item><item><title>克雷斯波准备在亚洲冠军联赛决赛中与科威尔展开新的竞争</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/sports/soccer/crespo-ready-renew-kewell-rivalry-asian-champions-league-final-2024-05-10/</link><description>艾因队主教练埃尔南·克雷斯波与横滨水手队的哈里·科威尔在周六的亚洲冠军联赛决赛中再次交锋，这距离有史以来最戏剧性的欧洲冠军联赛决赛之一已经过去了 19 年。</description><pubDate>Fri, 10 May 2024 11:03:31 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/sports/soccer/crespo-ready-renew-kewell-rivalry-asian-champions-league-final-2024-05-10/</guid></item><item><title>两名英国人明年将受审，被控为中国从事间谍活动</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/uk/two-britons-face-trial-next-year-accused-spying-china-2024-05-10/</link><description>周五，两名英国人被告知，他们将于明年接受审判，罪名是为中国从事间谍活动，其中包括执政党保守党一位著名英国议员的前研究员。</description><pubDate>Fri, 10 May 2024 11:00:41 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/uk/two-britons-face-trial-next-year-accused-spying-china-2024-05-10/</guid></item><item><title>中国电动汽车制造商 Zeekr 在美国市场首次亮相，股价飙升近 35%</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/chinas-zeekr-set-debut-nyse-after-upsized-ipo-2024-05-10/</link><description>周五，Zeekr 的股价较首次公开募股价格上涨近 35%，这为这家电动汽车制造商带来了强劲的开局，这是自 2021 年以来首家中国公司在美国主要市场首次亮相。</description><pubDate>Fri, 10 May 2024 10:48:24 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/chinas-zeekr-set-debut-nyse-after-upsized-ipo-2024-05-10/</guid></item><item><title>早盘竞价：失业人数激增、英国央行转变、香港股市飙升拯救了五月</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/us/global-markets-view-usa-2024-05-10/</link><description>迈克·多兰 (Mike Dolan) 对美国和全球市场未来一天的展望</description><pubDate>Fri, 10 May 2024 10:02:13 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/us/global-markets-view-usa-2024-05-10/</guid></item><item><title>4月份中国汽车出口创历史新高，但国内销量下降</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/chinas-april-car-sales-swing-contraction-despite-nev-milestone-2024-05-10/</link><description>周五的数据显示，由于价格竞争加剧以及消费者在经济复苏不稳定的情况下对大件消费持谨慎态度，国内销量同比下滑 5.8%，中国 4 月份汽车出口飙升至历史新高。</description><pubDate>Fri, 10 May 2024 08:45:56 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/chinas-april-car-sales-swing-contraction-despite-nev-milestone-2024-05-10/</guid></item><item><title>中国表示坚决反对美国出口管制工具</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/china-says-it-firmly-opposes-us-export-control-tools-2024-05-10/</link><description>在美国出于国家安全考虑将37家中国企业列入贸易限制名单后，外交部发言人周五表示，中国坚决反对滥用美国实体清单等出口管制工具。</description><pubDate>Fri, 10 May 2024 08:24:15 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/china-says-it-firmly-opposes-us-export-control-tools-2024-05-10/</guid></item><item><title>Porch 在美国起诉中国建设银行再保险欺诈损失</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/finance/porch-sues-china-construction-bank-us-over-reinsurance-fraud-losses-2024-05-10/</link><description>美国保险和房屋检查软件提供商 Porch 集团正在起诉中国资产第三大银行中国建设银行 (CCB)，指控其实施“大规模欺诈”，给 Porch 造成“巨大损失”。</description><pubDate>Fri, 10 May 2024 08:20:41 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/finance/porch-sues-china-construction-bank-us-over-reinsurance-fraud-losses-2024-05-10/</guid></item><item><title>第五招：走自己的路</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/take-five/global-markets-themes-graphic-2024-05-10/</link><description>随着欧洲各地纷纷降息，全球央行开始摆脱困境，而美国的借贷成本可能会在更长时间内保持较高水平，从而提振美元。</description><pubDate>Fri, 10 May 2024 08:13:21 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/take-five/global-markets-themes-graphic-2024-05-10/</guid></item><item><title>中国军方称其在南海“击退”了美国驱逐舰</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/china-military-says-it-drove-away-us-destroyer-south-china-sea-2024-05-10/</link><description>解放军南部战区周五在一份声明中表示，中国军队严密监视并“驱离”了5月10日进入南海西沙群岛领海的哈尔西号驱逐舰。</description><pubDate>Fri, 10 May 2024 07:29:43 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/china-military-says-it-drove-away-us-destroyer-south-china-sea-2024-05-10/</guid></item><item><title>富士康第一季度利润从低基数跃升，人工智能推动增长</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/technology/foxconns-q1-profit-jump-low-base-ai-power-growth-2024-05-10/</link><description>全球最大的合同电子产品制造商台湾富士康预计将于周二报告称，由于人工智能服务器的强劲需求以及去年同期的低基数，第一季度利润将增长一倍以上。</description><pubDate>Fri, 10 May 2024 06:44:49 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/technology/foxconns-q1-profit-jump-low-base-ai-power-growth-2024-05-10/</guid></item></channel></rss>